Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.76,0:03:24.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 我們按原定計劃舉行集訓！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.01,0:03:25.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.72,0:03:30.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看看 目的是戰術和同步的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.39,0:03:30.35,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(700,500)\fs24\pos(160,613)}第11回
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.39,0:03:30.35,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(700,500)\pos(318,613)}變 異
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.35,0:03:33.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛結束戰鬥 他們還真有精神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.11,0:03:35.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相比之下…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.82,0:03:37.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 難受…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.23,0:03:40.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也會去操縱系統的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.78,0:03:42.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說了不用你上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.66,0:03:46.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們那麼精神才反而讓人擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.99,0:03:48.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同化現象是無法主動意識到的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.33,0:03:50.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要好好觀察他們
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.41,0:03:54.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 先擔心擔心自己怎麼樣啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.92,0:03:57.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛死了！
