Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.00,0:04:37.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯沒錯 不用客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.38,0:04:40.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 我又帶了一堆店裡的洋裝回來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.46,0:04:42.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真拿你沒辦法 之後穿給你看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.84,0:04:45.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好開心 你想穿哪件？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.05,0:04:48.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Alvis的制服也是我設計的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.39,0:04:49.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.51,0:04:51.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要再來一碗嗎 再來一碗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.02,0:04:52.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我裝大碗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.31,0:04:54.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就得這樣才行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.90,0:04:58.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽 你太鬧騰了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.57,0:05:02.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和以前的內核相比 這位還真是親切啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.65,0:05:03.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.36,0:05:05.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您說…親切？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.91,0:05:08.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論如何 內核的舉止沒有異常
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.66,0:05:11.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敵人分析得怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.04,0:05:15.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,關於個體代號為步行者的阿撒謝爾型
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.54,0:05:17.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其本體的所在位置依舊不明
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.92,0:05:19.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們正在全力查探
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.25,0:05:25.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,駕駛員的同化現象都被抑制了 沒有人需要治療
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.22,0:05:28.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有的機體在戰鬥中都發揮了SDP
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.35,0:05:32.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即敵人的力量——超次元現象
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.35,0:05:32.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(796,655)}Super Dimensional Power
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.60,0:05:37.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mk.Ⅻ表現為機體再生及伴隨其中的同化現象
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.02,0:05:43.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mk.Ⅸ表現為類似Mk.Sein的龐大的能量增幅現象
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.57,0:05:47.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,月讀命表現為施展超強度護壁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.11,0:05:50.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,素盞嗚尊表現為基於零次元移動的空間跳躍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.45,0:05:55.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天照表現為提取遠處的物體
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.25,0:06:00.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另外 在駕駛員與機體的交換實驗中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.38,0:06:03.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,SDP發生改變並弱化了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.67,0:06:04.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼改變？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.01,0:06:10.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,例如水鏡美三香搭乘Mk.Ⅸ時 生成了不穩定的護壁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.68,0:06:15.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反過來 西尾里奈搭乘月讀命時 出現低級別的增幅現象
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.48,0:06:19.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,換句話說 機體的SDP取決於駕駛員
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.81,0:06:22.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有駕駛員搭乘其最適機體時才能發揮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.44,0:06:24.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人成為了扳機
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.61,0:06:26.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像戈耳狄俄斯結晶那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.61,0:06:26.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(600,655)}Gordius
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.65,0:06:30.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那東西產生了皆城乙姬和烏爾德之泉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.45,0:06:33.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用以和Mir交流
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.53,0:06:36.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而現在 他喚醒了皆城織姬
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.79,0:06:39.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給予了我們戰鬥的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.58,0:06:44.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,分析敵人的同時 抓緊查明樞要區域內發生的現象
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.21,0:06:49.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先於敵人瞭解彼此的力量是勝利的關鍵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.02,0:07:00.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼戈耳狄俄斯結晶現在出現了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.65,0:07:05.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我反問你 Alvis和法芙娜的形態為什麼變化不大？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.15,0:07:09.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那已經是我們最尖端的技術了 無從改變
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.82,0:07:11.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果改變了 理由會是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.07,0:07:13.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,與未知文化的接觸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.41,0:07:17.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說 你的言下之意是人類軍的到來改變了島？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.95,0:07:19.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這沒什麼大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.33,0:07:23.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,問題在於新的個體會來到這顆星球
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.67,0:07:28.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,島在對新Mir起反應嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.67,0:07:31.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全世界的Mir碎片都在起反應
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.64,0:07:34.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都在尋找未來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.93,0:07:38.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尋找毀滅之外的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.77,0:07:41.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毀滅…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.77,0:07:45.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芹 快過來 芹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.57,0:07:48.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了 什麼事 織姬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.07,0:07:51.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我一起洗澡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.40,0:07:52.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦…好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.98,0:08:25.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.81,0:08:26.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.11,0:08:28.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我吃好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.90,0:08:30.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.07,0:08:31.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.70,0:08:38.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二次L計劃提案書…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.20,0:08:41.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又要提交這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.12,0:08:44.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次由你爸爸去交
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.67,0:08:46.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然要覆核一遍就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.92,0:08:50.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真壁司令應該沒考慮這些吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.17,0:08:53.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的 我們會保護大家的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.18,0:08:56.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那文件很重要 給我放邊上去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.35,0:08:59.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.77,0:09:04.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 打擾你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.33,0:09:23.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸媽媽都想去找姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.29,0:09:26.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明姐姐已經不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.71,0:09:36.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果姐姐回來 我們一家人是不是就能破鏡重圓了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.72,0:09:43.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.90,0:09:57.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通過會議…技術…？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.70,0:10:03.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了 交給鏑木好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.99,0:10:08.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼搞的 最近好睏…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.59,0:10:21.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從技術視角相互確認效果…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.08,0:10:47.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.00,0:10:55.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不准看！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.18,0:11:05.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請借我件衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.06,0:11:09.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我吃飽了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.64,0:11:13.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我買了御門家的蛋糕 吃不吃？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.98,0:11:15.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 吃不吃呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.82,0:11:16.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一人一半好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.23,0:11:17.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.82,0:11:20.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.20,0:11:23.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是工作…或者說駕駛法芙娜的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.41,0:11:26.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一點事都沒有 再說我們都超強的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.91,0:11:29.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊 美三香真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.50,0:11:31.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要老師也誇你很勇敢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.04,0:11:35.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實我都記不清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.34,0:11:38.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺就像在做夢一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.13,0:11:43.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那種就算特別疼也醒不過來的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.06,0:11:48.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然其實也沒怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.27,0:11:52.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但總是常常覺得會發生不好的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.65,0:11:57.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美三香？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.90,0:11:59.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美三香！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.99,0:12:04.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你等著 媽媽馬上救你出來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.33,0:12:14.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又承蒙你款待了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.88,0:12:17.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正我一個人也吃不了這麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.71,0:12:20.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然做得不如一騎就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.34,0:12:21.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪有的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.22,0:12:23.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且像這樣坐在飯桌前
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.01,0:12:26.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就會想起世界還和平的那些日子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.44,0:12:35.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道那些孩子們…有沒有事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.61,0:12:39.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信他們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.23,0:12:41.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們也都長大了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.66,0:12:45.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.04,0:12:56.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.35,0:13:12.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快把美三香弄出來啊 拜託你們了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.27,0:13:15.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,SDP未經機體介入就發生了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.06,0:13:17.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上把樞要區域負責人叫來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.19,0:13:18.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.24,0:13:26.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,零央？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.53,0:13:27.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御門？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.91,0:13:29.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空間跳躍嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.20,0:13:31.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到 到底怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.83,0:13:32.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.45,0:13:34.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是美三香你家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.33,0:13:37.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,零央 你從哪過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.54,0:13:38.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.50,0:13:39.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道為什麼 身體自己就…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.05,0:13:42.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在哭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.71,0:13:45.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒…咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.05,0:13:48.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會這樣呢 好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.64,0:13:53.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是法芙娜使出來的東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.02,0:13:54.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你做的？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.02,0:13:58.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不太清楚 可能是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.40,0:14:03.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為你總是碰到可怕的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.36,0:14:03.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.44,0:14:05.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從同步中可以感覺到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.82,0:14:10.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每次都是你或者彗最先對上敵人 會怕也正常
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.33,0:14:14.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣嗎 我在害怕嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.50,0:14:21.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總覺得有一天會發生不好的事 雖然不太明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.21,0:14:27.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會把衝向你的敵人全都殺掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.01,0:14:29.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定會待在你身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.14,0:14:32.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 不要哭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.40,0:14:42.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人家沒哭啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.49,0:14:48.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 這個不能收回去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.20,0:14:51.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,零央你把它切開唄
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.82,0:14:52.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別為難人了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.04,0:15:02.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美三香…美三香！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.46,0:15:04.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒事吧 身上不痛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.13,0:15:05.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}媽媽 我喘不過氣了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.30,0:15:06.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,急死媽媽了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.55,0:15:08.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}沒事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.80,0:15:08.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.63,0:15:10.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我這邊也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.47,0:15:13.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊不 不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.43,0:15:16.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 保險起見
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.31,0:15:18.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最好還是讓他們都接受一下檢查
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.93,0:15:21.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會把裙子洗好再還給您的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.35,0:15:22.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.23,0:15:24.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.32,0:15:28.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次再幹這種事 看我不斃了你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.40,0:15:30.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.63,0:15:51.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走人了 還不快起來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.61,0:16:06.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,織姬 下手再輕點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.02,0:16:07.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去抓下一隻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.21,0:16:28.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.67,0:16:30.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美三香 把這個帶上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.88,0:16:33.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是零央落下的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.63,0:16:34.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.76,0:16:40.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,零央我倒是沒意見 為人又認真
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.39,0:16:42.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,個子很快就會長起來的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.27,0:16:43.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.65,0:16:47.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐喜阿姨 總是麻煩您了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.94,0:16:50.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,客氣什麼 反正一直都空著
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.61,0:16:52.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人來住的話 房子也會高興的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.07,0:16:55.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.91,0:17:04.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 駕駛員集訓現在開始
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.96,0:17:07.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先請劍司前輩說幾句話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.75,0:17:10.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家應該都聽說了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.17,0:17:14.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搭乘機體時發生的現象在平時也發生了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.13,0:17:16.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然檢查並沒有發現異常
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.59,0:17:19.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是如果彼此發現什麼不對勁的地方就馬上通知我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.47,0:17:19.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽明白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.26,0:17:21.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.11,0:17:32.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早苗…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.03,0:17:41.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,信號確認 是島的高速聯絡機「隼風」 代號「曉」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.37,0:17:42.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開始引導
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.88,0:17:50.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以上就是截至目前的報告
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.42,0:17:52.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,改變島的航向
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.46,0:17:54.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不再追加派遣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.84,0:17:57.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由整座島去接他們
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.51,0:18:03.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我餓扁了 飯還沒好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.85,0:18:06.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人數這麼多 你也來幫忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.56,0:18:07.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遵命遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.19,0:18:09.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家一起吃飯真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.44,0:18:12.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你家不是有你爸媽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.52,0:18:13.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直都是一個人吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.57,0:18:15.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸媽媽都很忙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.19,0:18:19.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算偶爾早回來也是一頭窩進房間裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.53,0:18:21.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞什麼 這不是很不正常嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.37,0:18:27.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐喜阿姨 怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.71,0:18:30.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外派部隊捎來的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.79,0:18:33.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人類和Mir在同一片土地上生活
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.47,0:18:41.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是口古井
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.18,0:18:44.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是艾梅莉安放Mir碎片的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.49,0:18:59.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在 我們和兩萬名倖存者一起出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.28,0:19:02.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道這會是一段怎樣的旅途
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.49,0:19:05.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我相信我們一定能到達希望之地
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.66,0:19:12.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個島…真的很和平呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.54,0:19:14.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是輸給敵人 我們也會是那樣的下場
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.71,0:19:17.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是傻瓜 居然陪著人類軍出發
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.09,0:19:19.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這也是為了島
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.51,0:19:22.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之 還好大家都沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.26,0:19:25.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們就做好我們能做的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.35,0:19:28.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 今天就先睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.52,0:19:33.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,零央 你在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.23,0:19:36.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給 你落在我家的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.07,0:19:39.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,裡面的東西 你看過了嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.49,0:19:41.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？裡面有東西嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.57,0:19:43.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼也沒有！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.20,0:19:47.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美香美香 女生睡二樓 快上來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.45,0:19:48.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.58,0:19:51.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安 零央
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.25,0:19:52.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.42,0:19:56.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也還能戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.59,0:19:58.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回過神來 就已經在想這些了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.55,0:20:01.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也沒資格責怪一騎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.72,0:20:03.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基本上也快開不動了就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.76,0:20:09.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在 培養後輩才是我們的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.64,0:20:12.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.46,0:20:37.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,駕駛員包場
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.63,0:20:39.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天這仗真輕鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.96,0:20:42.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是敵人現在攻過來估計就要輸了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.09,0:20:44.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你道行不夠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.22,0:20:51.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是敵人現在攻過來我們絕對輸…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.39,0:20:52.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.52,0:20:54.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們覺悟不夠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.39,0:20:56.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 要輸的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.03,0:21:03.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.20,0:21:06.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,織姬 你幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.87,0:21:08.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個是我的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.45,0:21:12.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你幹嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.66,0:21:13.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挺適合你的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.66,0:21:15.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個是我的啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.42,0:21:18.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才剛下戰場 他們還真是精神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.05,0:21:24.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.43,0:21:26.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.72,0:21:29.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,近藤醫生！你看這個！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.43,0:21:33.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.31,0:21:39.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里奈前輩 在這種地方睡覺可要感冒的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.98,0:21:41.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 里奈前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.86,0:21:45.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.36,0:21:47.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.20,0:21:51.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同化現象？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.29,0:21:53.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.25,0:21:54.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站住！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.83,0:21:57.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼也別碰！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.46,0:22:03.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里奈前輩？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.34,0:22:03.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里奈？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.97,0:22:11.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人類的姿態 心靈 生活…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.39,0:22:14.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你將會懂得
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.77,0:22:18.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要仍渴望戰鬥 就將面臨越來越多的失去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.48,0:22:23.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們尋求著未來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.48,0:22:28.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尋求著哪怕能少一點失去的未來
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（ED）
